<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太热了。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在体育馆里用笔记本扇风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，我不停流汗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可我只是站在这里。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脚边放了一个大冷藏箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我买了草莓、香蕉、桃子、牛奶和冰淇淋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要做一个冰凉的甜品。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶昔！” 莉琪边跳边喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。” 波比握着拳说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……我喜欢桃子奶昔。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森看着冷藏箱里的冰淇淋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶昔很容易做。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只需要把食材放进搅拌机，然后……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搅拌、搅拌、搅拌！” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜念出第一步。“把草莓放进搅拌机。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后放进一根香蕉。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和一杯桃子。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来，放一杯半香草冰淇淋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定很好吃。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把冰淇淋舀到量杯里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后放一杯半冰块。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，冷藏箱真凉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后加半杯牛奶。” 莉琪小心地倒下去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！已经完成了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快要完成了。” 雪莉老师纠正她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，你可以把搅拌机的盖子盖上，启动机器吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森盖上盖子，启动机器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>搅拌机的刀片旋转着，发出很大的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们听到冰块搅碎，撞到玻璃的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，声音变小了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奶昔做好了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给尼娜、波比和莉琪倒满了冰凉的奶昔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到贾森时，贾森突然把他的手盖在杯子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！” 他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，怎么了？你不想喝奶昔吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要。” 他摇摇头，又说了一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都看着贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么不喝呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对啊，真的很好喝。” 莉琪说完喝了一口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其实我不喜欢牛奶。” 贾森的眼睛往下看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不喜欢冰淇淋。我就是这么奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不奇怪。” 波比笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……你是有点儿奇怪，但不是因为这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很奇怪。小孩子应该喜欢牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小孩子应该喜欢冰淇淋。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小孩子不需要喜欢什么。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做水果冰沙也很容易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们只需要用果汁代替牛奶和冰淇淋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在冷藏箱里找了找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！这里正好有芒果汁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一起把草莓、香蕉、桃子、冰块和果汁倒进搅拌机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不到一分钟，贾森的水果冰沙就做好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢大家。” 他尝了一口，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！冰沙很好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>